            "notes": "The deck revolves around utilizing a mix of countermagic, burn spells, and efficient creatures to apply early pressure on the opponent. With Spider-Man 2099 as the commander, the goal is to control the board and disrupt the opponent's game plan while steadily chipping away at their life total. The deck includes a variety of instant-speed spells like Lightning Bolt, Counterspell, and Spell Pierce to handle threats efficiently and protect your own creatures. Additionally, the deck includes powerful creatures like True-Name Nemesis and Snapcaster Mage for added versatility and resilience. The mana base is carefully crafted to ensure consistent access to the necessary colors and lands for the game plan to succeed."
